data.description: Welcome home to an exceptional 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom, and 2-kitchen home in beautiful Chicago, IL. This gem is ready for your finishing touches boasting over 2900 total square feet of living space and siting on a generous 3500 square foot lot.   Step inside and discover a one-of-a-kind layout that's much larger than it appears from the outside. The main level showcases beautifully refinished original hardwood floors, adding timeless charm to the home. The fully finished basement is a true highlight, featuring a separate living room, family room, and kitchen, offering endless possibilities for entertaining or creating a private retreat.  With the convenience of a 2-car attached garage, parking is a breeze. Whether you're hosting gatherings or simply enjoying everyday living, this home provides the space and versatility you've been searching for.  This property offers an incredible opportunity to own a spacious and well-maintained home in a prime location. Don't miss out on the chance to make this your own slice of Chicago living. Schedule a showing today and envision the possibilities that await in this remarkable home.
